{"tid":1468217,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分化係病，禮貌係藥！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:58:26.000Z","uid":202592,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"613077b59db2782521a1fe365cfbc5ad54c7ceef","tid":1468217,"uid":202592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"分化係病，禮貌係藥！！！要醫病就要有藥去醫。<br />\n<br />\n相信各位巴絲睇到一大堆唔同意見直接飛埋黎，對情緒影響好大，各位手足對今日既行動有好多唔同意見，但文字上既語氣真係好需要大家既禮貌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「又話不分化，不割蓆，而家阻到遊客就屌晒鬼」<br />\n相信以上例子出現係好多POST到。<br />\n<br />\n好多巴打都開過POST話比意見同割蓆係完全兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係當措辭上既分別，就極容易引起唔同人既誤會，睇睇以下例子：<br />\n<br />\n例子1:<br />\n「屌你老母咪撚塞住D遊客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，阻到人又無撚用，唔係話你地係鬼，但唔該真係比少少腦，<span style=\"color: red;\">塞遊客係下策黎，XXX...</span> 利申：不分化不割蓆」<br />\n<br />\n「今日見到好多義士主動塞住遊客離港，好多謝大家既行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家行動完左同大家分析少少利弊。 <span style=\"color: red;\">個人認為覺得人少主動塞遊客離港都係XXX...</span>」<br />\n<br />\n例子2:<br />\n「屌你又話要塞爆機場，而家有義士去塞遊客就屌晒鬼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲話好意思不割蓆不分化。<span style=\"color: red;\">而家塞住遊客機場可以XXX</span>」<br />\n<br />\n「今日好多手足辛苦左成日，為左塞爆機場出好多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家明白塞住遊客可以令到XXX</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>紅字先係成段文字入面最重要既內容。如果各位巴絲真係希望傳達自己意見比其他人，保持好既禮貌非常重要。</strong>原因係:<br />\n1. 可以減少其他巴絲既負面情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 更容易令其他人接受之後既內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以就算心入面屌晒鬼都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n虛偽少少多加幾句禮貌說話</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左提高討論既氣氛，令到大家情緒更加正面，更加有助去交流意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論係有任何既意見，希望咁多位巴絲開每個POST，每個回覆都盡量保持多D禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁容易望到其他揩辭強硬既發言，就比佢影響到自己都開始屌人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebea2840d0b695705ddef919ccf20dcdc6958997","tid":1468217,"uid":202592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2887f603ec3969301d9be67b4df263fda07586a3","tid":1468217,"uid":202592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"858d4ded053ac517081bdb9e997bb1dfffc5beea","tid":1468217,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要檢討 善後 唔係互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻保持冷靜 獨立思考！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該大家檢討行動唔好用d鬧人既語氣 字眼！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEnyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEnyS</a></span>"},{"pid":"4800937727c27ae270d7f2355d0f78f903dfd346","tid":1468217,"uid":202592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabf876fc476c914272d450e8503ecfbe8f053dd","tid":1468217,"uid":202592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:15:02.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a95b7fc3372f622a11957f319844b0e2d0d9c2","tid":1468217,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:56.000Z","msg":"真心<br />\n禮貌真係消失咗<br />\n自721前後，見大家情緒都好易著，好易好燥<br />\n郁啲就屌人老母，係前面望到聽到係幾反感<br />\n好似出黎發洩咁<br />\n情緒無錯好易被帶動，但有啲時候真係需要反思自己言論，係咪對大家有幫助，出得黎嘅都比家人親，咁做咩仲要惡言，係有班煩膠，冷處理都未嘗不可，更莫講而家咁多狗咁多黑社會入黎帶風，製造黑材料，大家更要小心，某啲行動真喺要做，兄弟有事一定要救，但私刑參唔參與請個人衡量結果影響"},{"pid":"4dae54bc9c23f6ce4f2be1fbe5702bb003122c23","tid":1468217,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:10.000Z","msg":"遇鬼時<br />\n<br />\n1）先捉，<br />\n<br />\n2）圍大圈，分隔 同比多d 記者同人映隻鬼，<br />\n<br />\n個個企到密，根本映唔到。<br />\n<br />\n如鬼或自己人有受傷，都要拍片搵在場醫護幫忙<br />\n<br />\n自己傷固之然要醫護， 亦要係記者前問鬼有冇受傷或身體不適，搵在場醫護幫忙做初步檢查，盡番人道立場同道德高地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）搵記者影記錄，重點指出隻鬼做左乜野犯罪行為如打人，煽動，藏有危險品之類，所以採訪101拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n有物證就映埋物證。同令佢身分曝光，唔好祈望隻鬼會自爆，如果你諗住全世界鏡頭前嚴刑迫供，咁根本係另類送人頭，更何況打死隻鬼，相信佢都唔會講。<br />\n<br />\n闡明你嘅行為係合法性同正當性，同有需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）同時搵議員，叫議員處理/議員報警處理。<br />\n相信10多其9都上白車，popo都放人。<br />\n<br />\n重點係，你留住隻鬼冇乜用，只會令現場仲難控制仲亂，好似今日咁，好易比其他鬼去分化，阻醫護阻記者，<br />\n<br />\n如只做1-4，我知大家可能會好嬲，想發洩，但係隻鬼重點係要佢曝光比世界，囉資料，囉更多頻譜，依個先更有利。<br />\n<br />\n你唔好忘記一舉一動既然係鏡頭前，就要有鏡頭禮儀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒有最好的方法，要有改善的辦法"},{"pid":"fc7e01ebe6d1f1e3baadeeb3e987d143f648745d","tid":1468217,"uid":299860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5a0cc4567389243488c5348306d3f97688f47fa","tid":1468217,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要檢討 善後 唔係互屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻保持冷靜 獨立思考！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該大家檢討行動唔好用d鬧人既語氣 字眼！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEnyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEnyS</a></span>"},{"pid":"0a4092470267b588529d1da3ee061ff628b2573f","tid":1468217,"uid":4298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:08.000Z","msg":"我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗 (下集)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464134</a><br />\n<br />\n各位重睇一次啦<br />\n黑衫都唔洗著 <br />\n口號都唔洗叫<br />\n文宣都唔洗做<br />\n人多就知咩事"},{"pid":"2f126d600a917bdc605291a3af2fcce56ef802e7","tid":1468217,"uid":85290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:57:12.000Z","msg":"今晚機場單野，大家真係要醒 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468119/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468119/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1dee1f463671bdeeb32345795f60862f067e7a9b","tid":1468217,"uid":179679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}